title: Apple releases second iOS 26.3 beta for iPhone
summary: Apple has released the second iOS 26.3 beta for iPhone. The first beta introduced an easier way to switch between Android and iPhone, tweaks to the Astronomy and Weather wallpaper gallery, and more. more…

title: Open-Meteo is a free and open-source weather API for non-commercial use
El Niño was linked to famines in Europe in the early modern period
summary: A study of 160 European famines between 1500 and 1800 shows that El Niño weather events led to the onset of some famines and extended the duration of others
